text: Giorgi Kekelidze (; born 10 April 1984) is a Georgian poet, essayist and the founder of the first Georgian digital library lib.ge. From March 2012, he is a general director of the National Parliamentary Library of Georgia.Giorgi Kekelidze. National Library of Georgia.
